  "description": "The heartbeat at 11,000 meters. Sub-sub oscillator (-2 oct) as the sole voice — subOctMix maxed, fundamental nearly silent. Hydrostatic compressor at 0.85 creates rhythmic pumping from its own amplitude: the sound breathes by compressing itself. Darkness filter at 80 Hz removes everything except the physical sensation of pressure. Play C1 and feel your chest cavity resonate.",
