    "flock_note": "The Bone confirmed: monophonic sub-sub at ~3% CPU. The Ear heard chest compression at C1. The Tongue found velocity at 0.9 opens the filter just enough to let the fundamental ghost through — the heartbeat quickens under pressure.",
    "diagnosis": "This sound was a sub bass. It is now a pulse from the earth's mantle. The difference is that the -2 octave sub is the voice, not the reinforcement."
